This paper is likely to belong to the Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) sub-category as it discusses the InfiniBand interconnect, which is a type of network technology. It may also belong to the Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC) sub-category as InfiniBand is often used in high-performance computing clusters. Additionally, the paper discusses the OFED package, which is related to operating systems (cs.OS) and programming languages (cs.PL). Finally, the paper provides guidance on how to interact with the verbs API, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE).
